show.sharing_text_v2:
हेलो! मैंने Kuku FM (Android)  पर यह शो सुना और मुझे यकीन है कि आपको भी यह जरूर पसंद आएगा। 
https://links.kukufm.com/E5fgLb
show.description: In a world of wealth, ego, and arrogance, little Aarya’s innocent prank spirals into a fight between life and death. While her heartbeat slips away in the hospital, the only doctor who can save her is trapped on the road, blackmailed, humiliated by a ruthless couple blinded by pride. As every second counts, shocking truths unfold, the child fighting for life may be their own daughter. Will redemption come in time… or will their cruelty cost them the one thing they can never replace? Watch Now!
